data.description: Welcome to your urban oasis! This nice 3-bedroom, 1-and-a-half-bathroom home nestled in the heart of the city offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and convenient living. Located just minutes away from the vibrant downtown area, this home is a haven for urban dwellers seeking both style and accessibility.  Step inside and be greeted by the open living area, adorned with a contemporary fireplace that creates a warm and inviting ambiance. The open kitchen, overlooking the quaint backyard boasts offers stainless steel appliances, and incorporates an area to have a dining space or make the kitchen larger.  There are two cozy bedrooms on the second floor and a bath and a half, making morning a breeze.  The third-floor space provides a 3rd bedroom with an additional bonus room which could be used as flex space, office space, nursery, etc.   With 1 #xbd; baths, mornings are a breeze, and guests are always comfortably accommodated. The stylish bathrooms are adorned with modern fixtures and elegant tile work, offering a spa-like experience right at home.  Outside, there is a private backyard that provides a perfect spot for enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding with a glass of wine in the evening, all while soaking in the urban energy that surrounds you.  Additionally, the proximity to downtown means you're never far from the city's best dining, shopping, and entertainment options. Whether you're exploring trendy boutiques, indulging in gourmet cuisine, or attending cultural events, everything you desire is just a stone's throw away.  This 3-bedroom, 1 #xbd;-bathroom city home is more than just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Embrace the convenience of urban living without sacrificing comfort or style. Welcome to a home where modern elegance meets city living at its finest.
